{"name": "odoo14-addon-sale-discount-display-amount", "metadata": {"name": "odoo14-addon-sale-discount-display-amount", "version": "14.0.2.1.0", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 14.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/sale-workflow", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo"], "summary": "This addon intends to display the amount of the discount computed on sale_order_line and sale_order level", "upload_time": 1697706317}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fsale--workflow-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/sale-workflow\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/sale-workflow/tree/14.0/sale_discount_display_amount\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/sale-workflow-14-0/sale-workflow-14-0-sale_discount_display_amount\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/sale-workflow&target_branch=14.0\n    ```\n---\n\n# Sale Discount Display Amount\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:a4d5e8bdbaf927588ba0dbd66f511f5d42c8d76b92c7a4b0e8145deb22d222ee\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nIn standard Odoo only display the rate of the discount applied, never the\namount. It could be great to be able to tell the customer how much he spares.\nThis is the goal of this addons, it will show on a sale\norder the total without the discount and the value of the discount.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Configuration\n\nTo configure this module, you need to:\n\n1. Go to Sales/Settings and check \"Allow discounts on sales order lines\"\n2. Also check \"Display Total without discount in report\" in order to add this field to report.\n\n## Usage\n\nTo use this module, you need to:\n\n1. Go on a sale order\n2. Set a discount on a line\n3. The value of the discount is dislayed in the total section as well as the total without it.\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/sale-workflow/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/sale-workflow/issues/new?body=module:%20sale_discount_display_amount%0Aversion:%2014.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- ACSONE SA/NV\n\n### Contributors\n\n- C\u00e9dric Pigeon \\<<mailto:cedric.pigeon@acsone.eu>>\n- Abraham Anes \\<<mailto:abrahamanes@gmail.com>>\n- Chafique Delli \\<<mailto:chafique.delli@akretion.com>>\n- Manuel Regidor \\<<mailto:manuel.regidor@sygel.es>>\n- PyTech SRL \\<<mailto:info@pytech.it>>\n- Ooops404 \\<<mailto:info@ooops404.com>>\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/sale-workflow](https://github.com/OCA/sale-workflow/tree/14.0/sale_discount_display_amount) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.sale_discount_display_amount.models", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.sale_discount_display_amount.models.res_company", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.sale_discount_display_amount.models..res_company", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.sale_discount_display_amount.models.res_config_settings", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.sale_discount_display_amount.models..res_config_settings", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.sale_discount_display_amount.models.sale_order", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.sale_discount_display_amount.models..sale_order", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.sale_discount_display_amount.models.sale_order_line", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.sale_discount_display_amount.models..sale_order_line", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.sale_discount_display_amount.models.res_company", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.sale_discount_display_amount.models.res_company.ResCompany", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.sale_discount_display_amount.models.res_company.ResCompany._inherit", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.sale_discount_display_amount.models.res_company.ResCompany.report_total_without_discount", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instan